### Get author statistics (author id 1)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/stats/author/1

### Get author statistics (author id 2)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/stats/author/2

### Get author statistics — not found
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/stats/author/999

### Search blogs by keyword
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/stats/search?q=rust

### Search blogs — another keyword
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/stats/search?q=axum

### Search blogs — no results
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/stats/search?q=python
